item.title: CVE-2018-17935|2024-09-16T20:27:41.320Z -- telecrane -- f25%20series
item.description: All versions of Telecrane F25 Series Radio Controls before 00.0A use fixed codes that are reproducible by sniffing and re-transmission. This can lead to unauthorized replay of a command, spoofing of an arbitrary message, or keeping the controlled load in a permanent "stop" state.
